Plot a vaf spectrum

Source: R/plot_vaf.R
plot_vaf.Rd

Plot a VAF spectrum where clusters are colored by stick membership or mutation SBS cause

Usage

plot_vaf(muts, vaf_cut = 0.02, color_by = "stick")

Arguments

muts

Mutation table where causes and/or stick membership of mutations are annotated.

vaf_cut

Lower bound on VAF (defalt: 0.2).

color_by

Specify whether to color mutations by stick membership or SBS cause. It can be "stick" or "SBS" (default: "stick").

Value

A ggplot plot.

Examples

sim <- new(Simulation)
sim$update_tissue("Liver", 2e3, 2e3)

sim$add_mutant(name = "A",
               growth_rates = 1,
               death_rates = 0)
sim$place_cell("A", 1e3, 1e3)
sim$run_up_to_size("A",1e4)
#>
